high_descs: Go to the counter in front of you to the right of the stove.
Pick up the fork next to the salt shaker.
Put the fork into the mug to the left of the salt shaker.
Pick up the mug and fork.
Turn to your left and then go to the sink on your left.
Place the mug and fork into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a fork inside into the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk until you hit the counter.
Pick up the fork by the salt shaker.
Place the fork in the coffee mug to the left of the salt shaker.
Pick up the mug with the fork in it.
Turn left and walk until you line up with the sink then turn left and walk to the  sink.
Place the mug in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the counter space on the right of the stove.
Pick up the fork that is next to the salt shaker.
Place the fork inside the black mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug with the fork inside.
Turn and walk to the sink behind you.
Place the mug with the fork inside it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug and fork in the sink.
